    <description>

        <p>Katharsis is a simple GUI for the Kathara network emulation tool.</p>
        <p>It allows you to start and stop labs and connect to the containers in a convenient way.</p>
        <p>It allows you to conveniently open multiple container terminals next to each other.</p>
        <p>Katharsis requires Docker to be installed in rootful mode, and you have to be in the docker group.</p>

        <p>This app is written in Python and uses GTK 4, libadwaita, and VTE.</p>
    </description>

